{
  "texts": [
    "Multiple layered convolutional neural network sub-models were employed to diagnose COVID-19 based on these images.",
    "A softmax classifier was used to stack the submodels from the Xception and VGG19 models.",
    "To demonstrate the discriminating power of the stacked CNN model, 4645 CT scans from 65 patients were collected.",
    "Out of these, 2249 images were found to have COVID-19, while 2396 were assessed as being in excellent health.",
    "The stacked CNN model achieved a true positive rate of 97.62% for multi-class classification."
  ]
}